@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_irymnz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.77 / wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.13)))
    v1 = v2
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp))
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v1 + 0.09)) - (0.87 / wp.exp(tmp + 0.85)))
    tmp = (tmp + 0.37)
    v1 = wp.cos((0.96 * (tmp + 0.66 + tmp + 0.05)))
    tmp = wp.sin(tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
